    "name": "Tailgate",
    "steam_appid": 3046820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/406a729f8f94e2b2096ee710611b4695.poster.avif?t=1762800576\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/406a729f8f94e2b2096ee710611b4695.webm?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/406a729f8f94e2b2096ee710611b4695.mp4?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/b61dd9e1d8bd5fc0db0052d900d0db6e.webp?t=1762800576\" width=356 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as an aging labrador retriever named Hyde. One morning you wake up and realize that your Human, Derek, is gone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/acafee29a5746f91791b7a849cf9eb76.poster.avif?t=1762800576\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/acafee29a5746f91791b7a849cf9eb76.webm?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/acafee29a5746f91791b7a849cf9eb76.mp4?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get out of the house and explore the desolate yet beautiful fall surroundings of the San Pedro village. Use your dog’s senses, solve problems, and puzzles the doggo way. Search for hidden passages around obstacles and enemies, find long-lost balls that will remind you of precious moments, discover ancient dog lore, and finally pass through the mysterious Tailgate to find and save your Human.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/b32413e7392cefe2de915b418ad741eb.poster.avif?t=1762800576\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/b32413e7392cefe2de915b418ad741eb.webm?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/b32413e7392cefe2de915b418ad741eb.mp4?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/137efc207f6af3ce57f0aad7550b1de8.avif?t=1762800576\" width=736 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thousands of years ago ancient Dogs chose to accompany Humans on their journey, establishing a strong spiritual bond, the Kana. Connected through Kana they’ve been through thick and thin together. Through war, misery, desperation, illness, and other mishaps big and small, Dogs have never questioned Humans. Dog after dog, generation after generation, they were loyal to the human race. But as a wise dog said, loyalty is a two-way street. Kana was absorbing an immense amount of hate, doubt, pain, and suffering. The connection became so corrupted and fragile that it finally broke down, tearing the fabric of both Human and Canine worlds apart. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What exactly caused Kana's final corruption is unknown, but it must have been something truly terrible. Dogs have became feral, returning to their prehistoric forms or even worse. The Rift, however, for reasons no one yet understands, did not affect some of the dogs. One older, grumpy labrador in particular…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/c9ad400e02470b8da56469bdd4450e56.poster.avif?t=1762800576\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/c9ad400e02470b8da56469bdd4450e56.webm?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/c9ad400e02470b8da56469bdd4450e56.mp4?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/a4d6a6a5507bce50f947850a7af887b3.avif?t=1762800576\" width=696 height=157 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 7 different locations including village streets, an abandoned warehouse, stray dogs' Refuge, rural wilderness, and a mystical canine parallel world;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think and see like a dog — sniff for smell traces that will lead you to your objectives, important places, and items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to other animals that will help you on your journey with their unique abilities. A cat that can read (at least that's what she says), a diplomatic pug, a stray dog that will teach you survival skills, and many others.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect memory balls to discover the story of Hyde’s life, doggo wisdom, and ancient canine lore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replenish your stamina and gain temporary power-ups.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fool around like a dog would — play with balls, sticks, and stones, try to catch a cat, eat weird food, and go places that you normally would not dare to go.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/4c6d460913c084e4c062956219f4a5a0.poster.avif?t=1762800576\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/4c6d460913c084e4c062956219f4a5a0.webm?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/4c6d460913c084e4c062956219f4a5a0.mp4?t=1762800576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Put your tail where your mouth is and...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046820/extras/9dba28527617273785989faa1ce95fa9.avif?t=1762800576\" width=542 height=99 /></span></p>",
